com.schlimm.springcdi.interceptor.strategies.impl
Class ClassLevelBindingsVisitor

java.lang.Object
  com.schlimm.springcdi.interceptor.strategies.impl.ClassLevelBindingsVisitor

public class ClassLevelBindingsVisitor
extends Object

Check is the given BeanDefinition is intercepted by the given interceptor. If yes store that information in InterceptorInfo. Assumes that BeanDefinition is of type AnnotatedBeanDefinition.

Niklas Schlimm
